oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Alfred Councill and his four-point Tellico buck in Cherokee National Forest, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Tiptonville, Tenn. Man, Alfred Councill, and his four-point Tellico buck. Councill is wearing a cap, jacket and pants while holding his shotgun. The buck is hanging from a tree limb with an identifier tag tied to its antlers. There is tree brush and treeline in the background.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
